        "Eliminate foods high in protein from your diet.",
        "Reduce intake of foods high in potassium.",
        "Increase intake of sodium-containing food."
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "Reduce intake of foods high in potassium.",
      "explanationText": "",
      "explanationImage": null
    },
